				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Remember those top ten lists we all sent in a while back? 
<br />

<br />
It looks like Brenlo may be trying to updating us late next week, workload pending (hopefully) as to the classification of items.  1) Broken 2) Working as intended. From the looks of things we can pretty much guess what they will be but it's another additional step in getting these things resolved. Assuming that not everything on the list will be classified as "broken"  there may be some frustration but hopefully everyone can work thru the difference of opinion, debate and work to get our top 10 changes made ASAP; An interesting read on the shaman class boards:
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=shamanbalance&message.id=2160#M2160" target="_blank">http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=shamanbalance&message.id=2160#M2160</a>
<br />

<br />
and one on the mage boards:
<br />

<br />
