A bug in GoD trial #4 involving a pulled mob going in the opposite direction and aggroing 4-5 mobs in the pit (loc -65, -675, -35) then all mobs warping up to the group has been reported to CS and being looked into. Advise until this is fixed.... anyone pulling this area to pull into the tunnel vs. up to the corner of the room as dealing with 1/2 wanderers in the tunnel is better than having a whole bunch of mobs biting at your butts.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://members.cox.net/dtresendes/danisig.png" border="0" />
